snippet.title: PSX Longplay [471] Arthur to Astaroth no Nazomakaimura: Incredible Toons
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: SCHLAUCHI

This is pretty much a direct port of Dynamix's Sid & Al's Incredible Toons for the Playstation, but with the graphics changed to Ghouls 'n' Ghost's style! -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
